children.value: How to use this web app:
Enter a chord progression in the text box.
Squeal in delight, as the promised melodies are shown on the screen.
You can toggle the Help/Settings panel from the buttons to the right
Update this page with the complete chord dictionary, so users will know what kind of input is valid.
Default range is Bb3 to B5. Smoothness = total distance between the notes in the melody (in semitones). Range = distance between lowest note and highest note (in semitones).
Melodies are filtered/sorted by a few rules:
Range must be no greater than one octave
Only the 100 smoothest melodies are shown
